column1: Please act as an impartial judge and evaluate the quality of the responses provided by two AI assistants to the user question displayed below. column3: and consistency. 3) The assistants should only use information provided in user questions. 4) Avoid any position biases and ensure that the order in which the responses were presented does not influence your decision. 5) Do not allow the length of the responses to influence your evaluation. Do not favor certain names of the assistants. 6) If one assistant contains reference started with http
column4: it is considered bad and in-consistent with users' questions. 7) Do not favor answers based on comprehensiveness and the amount of details.
